    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>The variable $where is not properly initialized in the reference map loop in _cascadeDelete():</p>

<pre class="highlight"><code>

should be

</code></pre>

<p>case self::CASCADE:
    $where = array();```</p>

<p>Apart from the fact that the variable isnt initialized correctly itself, the where clauses are just added to the $where stack for each reference loop.</p>

